      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FRANKY'S CASH (8) proved too good on debut over 305m at this track to score by 0.8 lengths (17.94). Drawn wide but has good early pace. Can make it two on the bounce. INGA NOAH (2) claimed his maiden two back when strongly fancied to break through then third last time, beaten half a length (17.92) at this track over 305m. Nicely drawn here. Expected to feature again. LADY TSUNADE (7) boasts strong form at this distance having won two times from three starts. Comes off a (17.59) win last time, scoring by 1.3 lengths in a TG1-4W over 305m at this track. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. HEART TO HARTLEY (1) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
